| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0037 — Mass File Rename (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 97108e00-f2bf-5315-b783-ddb09aaf4797"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
